  "text": "The robustness assumption on C in Proposition 2.4 forces dim B C ≥ n − 1 and so this result only yields new information when s > n − 1. It is interesting to compare this result with Corollary 2.3 and the discussion thereafter in [CITATION_1] , which applies to self-affine systems where s ≤ 1.",
